{"tid":828529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年女巴士一人霸兩座位  遭斥責反舉機相向","createTime":"2018-09-19T17:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T00:42:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce23be72188a4f06aea9af16adcc9505e353cfa","tid":828529,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T17:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6BtpFa1bagG.Smxvn4e._g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ad393b34283e29f7a9a45166cdc80de4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6BtpFa1bagG.Smxvn4e._g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fad393b34283e29f7a9a45166cdc80de4&h=40ecba44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴士座位有限，乘客應該互諒互讓，絕對不應一人佔據兩個座位，或者影響他人就坐。不過有人卻只顧自己舒適，不理他人擠迫。有網民在巴士上發現一名中年女乘客坐在座位上，雙腳卻「飛象過河」，伸到對面座位下方，令其他乘客無法就坐。<br />\n<br />\n網民Eric在Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」上載影片，表示太太Ice在九龍灣，乘搭巴士213X線往秀茂坪，發現一名婆婆要將雙腳「吊在」通道，但卻無法掂地。她擔心萬一巴士急停，婆婆會發生危險，於是上前查看。<br />\n<br />\nIce走到座位之間的位置，發現一名中年女士將雙腳伸到對面座位下，才會令婆婆要將雙腳放出通道。她要求對方收起雙腳，但對方只顧低頭看電話並無任何回應。她近距離向該名中年女士揮手，惟對方依然不作理會，於是她開聲要求對方將腳縮開。對方仍然不為所動，更拿出手機對着Ice。<br />\n<br />\n東網聯絡到Ice，她表示曾考慮向車長投訴，但當時為放工時間，滿車乘客，擔心投訴後，車長可能要停車處理，「擔心會阻到其他人」，最後只好作罷。她表示雙腳未能掂地的阿婆其後落車，而直到自己到站時，該女子對面的位置都沒乘客可以坐下。有網民搞笑表示，「阿婆，究竟有咩驅使你對腳咁短都仲要夾硬伸長呢？」亦有人建議Ice強行坐下，讓對方知難而退。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nYi Wah Yeung：好佬怕爛佬，爛佬怕潑婦。以子之矛攻子之盾。<br />\n<br />\nArthur Lee：阿婆，究竟有咩驅使你對腳咁短都仲要夾硬伸長呢？"},{"pid":"e89ed8ebc0dfe5b65e2d308decf8569a1c2c95f6","tid":828529,"uid":91673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:07:47.000Z","msg":"一腳轟落去啦"},{"pid":"118723c0b41adc4caaaf3a2737638cb2206a9667","tid":828529,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:24:08.000Z","msg":"213x 經安達安泰"},{"pid":"50998c2924e2cbfd509ebd3ffd17bb844dcebe91","tid":828529,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:16:46.000Z","msg":"照坐落去囉"},{"pid":"34236bf94b2b63d1281374274424ea5c8604d168","tid":828529,"uid":60137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:25:50.000Z","msg":"斬撚左佢對閪腳落黎，講都費撚事"},{"pid":"1633c1af0c937cbadbf4c7f88d7b66583ebe9239","tid":828529,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:29:38.000Z","msg":"轉彎扮失衡一腳踩落去有無得諗"},{"pid":"24bcee3b2848d2bf3b7257553487746c2f8d98bf","tid":828529,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:31:04.000Z","msg":"大陸婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28fb18f8b7c5e42cf732e10c698bd77411ed501","tid":828529,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1633c1af0c937cbadbf4c7f88d7b66583ebe9239","tid":828529,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:29:38.000Z","msg":"轉彎扮失衡一腳踩落去有無得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"梗係有~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6a574f2bbc26cfae6f4359c1b9208057e478ff","tid":828529,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:42:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}